345
00:19:14,512 --> 00:19:16,125
<font class="speaker2" color="#33339f">The Angels Have Protected You.</font>

346
00:19:16,126 --> 00:19:18,062
<font class="speaker2" color="#33339f">From What These Beings Once Were.</font>

347
00:19:18,063 --> 00:19:19,676
<font color="#d4d4d4">Don't-</font>

348
00:19:19,677 --> 00:19:21,290
