<font color="#d4d4d4">[RANDOMPOS] Spores. [RANDOMPOS]</font>

357
00:19:34,203 --> 00:19:35,816
<font color="#d4d4d4">Hail our King.</font>

358
00:19:35,817 --> 00:19:37,430
<font class="speaker2" color="#33339f">Please Proceed.</font>

359
00:19:37,431 --> 00:19:39,000
<font class="speaker2" color="#33339f">Lest You Become Like Them.</font>

360
00:19:45,002 --> 00:19:47,042
<font color="#33339f">Allow Us To Explain.</font>

361
00:19:47,043 --> 00:19:49,900
<font color="#33339f">Those Who Disrespect Us Must Be Eradicated.</font>

362
00:19:49,901 --> 00:19:51,941
<font color="#33339f">We Are Harmony, Sense, Order.</font>

363
00:19:51,942 --> 00:19:54,390
<font color="#33339f">We Created Order In Form, "Space".</font>

364
00:19:54,391 --> 00:19:56,839
<font color="#33339f">We Created Order In Flow, "Time".</font>

365
00:19:56,840 --> 00:20:00,105
<font color="#33339f">Without Our Laws, Everything Will Revert To Chaos.</font>

366
00:20:00,106 --> 00:20:02,963
<font color="#33339f">Without These Lands, Existence Loses All Value.</font>

367
00:20:02,964 --> 00:20:05,004
<font color="#33339f">But They Defy Us.</font>

368
00:20:05,005 --> 00:20:07,045
<font color="#33339f">But They Desire The Opposite.</font>

369
00:20:07,046 --> 00:20:10,311
<font color="#33339f">They Don't See The Beauty Of Our Laws.</font>

370
00:20:10,312 --> 00:20:12,760
<font color="#33339f">They Consider These Laws "Shackles" Instead.</font>

371
00:20:12,761 --> 00:20:15,618
<font color="#33339f">Their Chaos Is Seeping Into These Lands.</font>

372
